@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title 命令结果标准结果流时序
hide footbox

actor "Ground Station\nController" as GS
participant "Protocol Runtime\nSession + Authority Gate" as RT #EEF2F4
participant "Vehicle Executor" as EX #F1F4F6

== Root Command ==
GS -> RT : Command.Goto\nmessage_id = 8101\ncorrelation_id = 8101

== Received ==
RT --> GS : CommandResult.Received\ncorrelation_id = 8101

== Accepted ==
RT -> EX : 调度执行\n目标匹配 + 权限检查通过
EX --> RT : 执行器接单
RT --> GS : CommandResult.Accepted\ncorrelation_id = 8101

== InProgress ==
EX --> RT : 执行中\nprogress = 60
RT --> GS : CommandResult.InProgress\nprogress_percent = 60

== Terminal ==
alt 成功完成
  EX --> RT : 执行完成
  RT --> GS : CommandResult.Succeeded\nprogress_percent = 100
else 失败或失效
  EX --> RT : 执行失败 / 取消 / 超时
  RT --> GS : CommandResult.Failed | Cancelled | Expired
end

note right of RT
读图重点：
- 所有结果都保持同一个 correlation_id
- Terminal 必须落到明确终态
- 失败路径替换的是终态，不是前置相位
end note
@enduml
